# Optional local-only strict audit denylist.
#
# Copy this file to .public-release-denylist.local and add private values that
# should never appear in tracked files. The .local file is gitignored.
#
# Lines are case-insensitive literal matches by default.
# Prefix with regex: for a Python regular expression.
#
# Examples with placeholders only:
# private-device-label
# regex:private-host-[0-9]+\.example\.internal
